events.text: you know what they say—“curiosity killed the cat.”
it sucks to prove such a cliche phrase right!
we didn’t suffer much, though. not sure if you remember, [PlayerName]. it came pretty quick.
or, ended pretty quick, i guess.
they looked sooo good though, red and juicy…
i’m beginning to think i didn’t learn anything from this experience. hah!
there aren’t any poisonous things up there, though! c’mon, let’s go!
